Definition: tormented or harassed by nightmares or unreasonable fears
Example: hagridden...by visions of an imminent heaven or hell upon earth- C.S.Lewis
Synonyms: hagridden, tormented, or, harassed, by, nightmares, unreasonable, fears, visions, of, an, imminent, heaven, hell, upon, earth, -, C, S, Lewis
Category: adj.all
